commit.message:
(STARTFILE_SPEC, ENDFILE_SPEC): Delete superfluous -pg tests.

(LINK_SPEC): Add libp directories to -Y when -pg.

From-SVN: r10258

files.patch:

-			  %{pg:gmon.o%s}}} \
-			%{pg:crti.o%s}%{!pg:crti.o%s} \

 			 %{traditional:values-Xt.o%s} \
